body:
Sup Mates.

Right, some people have wanted this to be updated, so after 2 weeks of overcoming classic Kiwi procrastination,  I have done just that!

I've been going through the old thread, and I've deleted all the inactive channels that used to be on here.
As you can see, only a few channels from that old list are still active.
So, if you would like me to put your channel on here, just post a link in the comments and I'll add you.

The only criteria is that you have to post Avicus related content on your Youtube channel, at least semi-regularly.  

Oh, and it'll have an order this time. Channels with a high subscriber count will be at the top.
I'll update the subscriber count thing every now and then.
Because it won't be constant, the subscriber count shown for each channel will be an approximation. 

It's just good to have some sort of order. It'll be better than the cluster fuck it was last time.

Why? Because I love you.
